{"tid":1755460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求未完架！響應廣告界，下星期搞一次全民大罷工！","createTime":"2019-11-25T15:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T21:06:40.000Z","uid":299647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5eec94e63b0a313794f36d444e8586154a1c4984","tid":1755460,"uid":299647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"各位我哋未完架，五大訴求要繼續落去！<br />\n<br />\n全靠之前咁多位手足，區議會一戰已經說明一切<br />\n民意歸我哋！<br />\n<br />\n下星期各行各業罷工要政府回應，<br />\n釋放所以被拘捕人士，<br />\n清算一班黑警，一挫佢哋銳氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><br />\n香港人 心不死<br />\n堅持五大訴求 缺一不可　<br />\n我們並肩前行 奪回香港<br />\n<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回所有暴動定性<br />\n3. 永不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴、包括612暴力清場、721警黑合流、811血腥鎮壓、831太子站撕殺列車<br />\n5. 全面落實真「雙普選」</strong>"},{"pid":"ea89e27e0c0a793b430f5baaf8ec62442d69bef6","tid":1755460,"uid":36808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家時間<br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以幫下車手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無言感激<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747239</a>"},{"pid":"b10e4c20d329bc0d25da6ae4da5faf4b8331462e","tid":1755460,"uid":42194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">區選贏左就等於抗爭完？NO!!!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bz7Zmw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbz7Zmw5.jpg&h=3ff0c310&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3nvTqYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3nvTqYM.jpg&h=00ee475c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感恩 &bull; 前行<br />\n《香港人權與民主法案》感恩節集會<br />\n<br />\n感謝美國通過法案 從速制裁黑警奸吏<br />\n<br />\n日期：28/11/2019 (Thu)<br />\n時間：19:00 - 21:30<br />\n地點：中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n主辦：大專學界國際事務代表團；民間感恩節集會團隊<br />\n<br />\n*已通知警方, 待發不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\nChannel：@ThanksUSA<br />\nGroup：@ThankyouUSA<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nThank you &amp; March on<br />\nThanksgiving Day Assembly for HRDA<br />\n<br />\nTo appreciate the U.S. Enactment of the Act<br />\nImmediate Sanction of Government Officials and Police Force<br />\n<br />\nDate：28/11/2019 (Thu)<br />\nTime：19:00 - 21:30<br />\nVenue：Edinburgh Place, Central<br />\nOrganizers：HKIAD；Thanksgiving Day Assembly Citizens Organising Committee<br />\n<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Pending Issuance<br />\n<br />\nChannel：@ThanksUSA<br />\nGroup：@ThankyouUSA<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區選贏左，法案過左，就代表贏左？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當然唔係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n下一步，國際線究竟打d咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期四晩見啦！<br />\n星期四晚愛丁堡要人！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcee25f78d9e12f367b2fa7e7a538e1d47936b01","tid":1755460,"uid":299647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5008a0f31ce9d41ad5de5a685578830e4380486","tid":1755460,"uid":299647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif